00:26:27.316 --> 00:26:29.266
So we're already
talking to one formatter,

00:26:29.606 --> 00:26:31.766
and we say sting
from this value.

00:26:33.136 --> 00:26:34.496
Well that worked fine
when this was a number,

00:26:34.496 --> 00:26:35.326
