00:26:35.596 --> 00:26:37.566
So now we need to talk to
the MeasurementFormatter.

00:26:37.566 --> 00:26:39.286
Now, it's a simple
one-word change.

00:26:40.286 --> 00:26:41.596
Otherwise, it's exactly
the same.

00:26:42.496 --> 00:26:43.736
Works the same for
