00:27:24.346 --> 00:27:25.426
which is our goal to start with.

00:27:26.216 --> 00:27:28.536
We need to show these
in real world units.

00:27:29.326 --> 00:27:33.226
So we could do some
conversion logic of our own,

00:27:33.716 --> 00:27:35.926
